  -qt-creator-3.4.1.ebuild:
  Version bump.

*qt-creator-3.4.1 (02 Jun 2015)

  02 Jun 2015; Davide Pesavento <pesa@gentoo.org> +qt-creator-3.4.1.ebuild,
  -qt-creator-3.4.0.ebuild:
  Version bump.

